    "xml": "#补充第25、26行代码，让选手c不留痕迹地来到合适的起跑位置\n#提示:左侧还有天空背景(bg3.png)和其他选手供你选择哦！\nfrom turtle import *\nfrom race import *\nfrom random import *\nScreen().bgpic(\"bg1.png\")\nas_ = randint(0,100)\na = Turtle()\nScreen().register_shape(\"可多.png\")\na.shape(\"可多.png\")\nbs = randint(0,100)\nb = Turtle()\nScreen().register_shape(\"兰朵.png\")\nb.shape(\"兰朵.png\")\n\nc = Turtle()\nScreen().register_shape(\"海龟.png\")\nc.shape(\"海龟.png\")\n\na.penup()\na.goto(0, 0)\nb.penup()\nb.goto(0, 60)\n#补充下面2行代码，让选手c不留痕迹地来到合适的起跑位置\nc.penup()\nc.goto(0,120)\ncs = randint(0,100)\nset_speed(a,as_)\nset_speed(b,bs)\nset_speed(c,cs)\n\ngame_start(a,b,c)\n\nScreen().bgpic(\"win.png\")\ngame_result()",
